      "rationale": "In-vitro test loop conditions (phosphate-buffered saline blood analog, 37°C, 3.5 L/min, 2400 RPM) were replicated in CFD boundary conditions within 1.5%. Fluid viscosity and density matched to within 0.8% of measured values. Test conditions adequately reproduced for the nominal validation point."
