    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation at the nominal operating point demonstrates CFD model accuracy within the 15% NIH acceptance band. Sensitivity analysis bounds input uncertainty contributions. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model is well-established for centrifugal blood pump CFD and has been validated at the design operating point. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is met across all five simulated operating conditions in the COU matrix, supporting the conclusion that the model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis conditions for regulatory submission.",
